EDGE - Empowering the Disabled through Guided E-Marketing


Play games and help the disabled community. In the true spirit of Singapore, buy one and get credits to play free. What do you buy? You get to buy soft or real artefacts created by the disabled community. Be they be in Singapore or anywhere else in the world.

Our community storefront caters to 3 distinct audiences: 1. Just let me play the games people, 2. Corporates with a social consience, 3. Candy Crushers wanting to trade our credis for Candy Crush lives.
